### Get All Users (Member)
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{member_token}}

### Get All Users (Admin)
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/users?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Get User by ID
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/users/{{user_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Create User (Admin only)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "userName": "newuser",
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "fullName": "New User"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("user_id", response.body.id);
%}

### Update User (Admin only)
PUT {{HostAddress}}/api/users/{{user_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "userName": "updateduser",
  "email": "updated@example.com",
  "fullName": "Updated User"
}

### Delete User (Admin only)
DELETE {{HostAddress}}/api/users/{{user_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

